Description: Manipulation of Microsoft Word and PowerPoint Documents
Function: as_base64
Parameters: x
Test patterns used: test_that
Expectations used: expect_equal, expect_error, expect_false, expect_length, expect_true

Function Code:
```r
as_base64 <- function(x) {
  if (!is.character(x)) {
    stop("'x' must be a character vector.")
  }
  z <- vapply(
    x,
    function(elem) {
      if (is.na(elem)) {
        NA_character_
      } else {
        base64_encode(charToRaw(elem))
      }
    },
    NA_character_
  )
  unname(z)
}
```

